    "description": "<br><strong>Welcome to western city simulator </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821500/extras/a6b4173f05d1bd1d2130583b1da4c7dd.poster.avif?t=1718407478\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821500/extras/a6b4173f05d1bd1d2130583b1da4c7dd.webm?t=1718407478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821500/extras/a6b4173f05d1bd1d2130583b1da4c7dd.mp4?t=1718407478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Complete missions and assignments for Western Rail Company on a planned railroad route.<br>Discover and restore abandoned cities and locations. Find out why cities were abandoned.<br>look for evidence and pieces of story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821500/extras/82e8a8be2b767065ccd337f5128bd2fe.poster.avif?t=1718407478\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821500/extras/82e8a8be2b767065ccd337f5128bd2fe.webm?t=1718407478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821500/extras/82e8a8be2b767065ccd337f5128bd2fe.mp4?t=1718407478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Build your dream western city.</strong><br>Solve citizens problems, provide support for railroad constructors and fulfill their requests<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821500/extras/859c9893461f3ee6738436e4dd653a41.poster.avif?t=1718407478\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shar