g_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821500/extras/83442f10b072da3c15d3ad938772c154.poster.avif?t=1718407478\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821500/extras/83442f10b072da3c15d3ad938772c154.webm?t=1718407478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821500/extras/83442f10b072da3c15d3ad938772c154.mp4?t=1718407478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Bring back to live ghost towns and solve the problems of the Wild West.</strong>",
